Package com.fortify.bugtracker.src.fod.processor

This package contains various composite IProcessor implementations and related classes for submitting FoD vulnerabilities to bug trackers or other external systems, and performing issue state management.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFoDSourceVulnerabilityProcessor
    This abstract IProcessor implementation provides some common functionality used by FoDSourceProcessorSubmitVulnsToTarget and FoDSourceProcessorUpdateVulnsOnTarget, like storing the FoDSourceVulnerabilitiesConfiguration, checking the Context, and providing FoD connection-related CLIOptionDefinition instances.
